page.title: 09Public houses in area
page.content:
{THE BELL:}Owned by the brewery {BENSKINS}-{IND COOPE.}It is a non commercial pub mainly used by the regulars from the village and the close surrounding areas.The pub has no attractions apart from a beer garden.The occupiers are Mr and Mrs Austin.There is a barbeque every weekend.
{THE FIGHTING COCK:} This is a commercial pub. modern pub.Its trade is greatly boosted due to the situation of it.It is right on the old A11.The Bell and The Fighting Cock do not compete with each other.
